{"actor":"jonah-cal","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-14T18:00:41Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":113,"issue_id":"road_to_riches-6pa","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"road_to_riches-6pa\",\"title\":\"[Epic] Property System (P0)\",\"description\":\"Implement P0 property mechanics: buying unowned shops, paying rent on opponent shops, investing in own shops, district ownership tracking. Includes rent/max-capital LUT formulas: Rent = LUT * BaseRent * (2*CurrentVal - BaseVal) / BaseVal, MaxCap = LUT * BaseVal - CurrentVal.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"jonahmt@berkeley.edu\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T06:16:41Z\",\"created_by\":\"jonah-cal\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T06:16:41Z\"}"}
